<HEAD>NOW Cotton Bowl Parade Will Expose Too Many Legs</HEAD>
<DATELINE>DALLAS (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The National Organization for Women is kicking up
a fuss over plans to lead off the Cotton Bowl Parade with 995 pairs
of women's legs.
   The local chapter is circulating a petition objecting to the use
of ``sex appeal and chauvinism'' in promoting the New Year's Day
